  <h1>A3  Sensitive Data Exposure</h1>
  <p class="muted">Exposure of secrets, credentials, or personal data due to weak protection or transit without HTTPS.</p>
  <h3>Mitigations</h3>
  <ul><li>Use HTTPS/TLS for all transport.</li><li>Encrypt sensitive fields at rest if required and avoid storing secrets in code.</li></ul>
  <h3>Where to patch</h3>
  <p>Review config files and any plaintext secrets; ensure password hashes are used.</p>
